I'm player Wang Yuwen.

516
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:45,840
In this case,

517
00:15:45,840 --> 00:15:47,520
I play An Xiaowen,
the eldest daughter of the An family.

518
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:48,380
(An Xiaowen,
eldest daughter of the An family)

519
00:15:48,640 --> 00:15:49,800
At the An family villa,

520
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:51,040
we were shooting for magazine.

521
00:15:51,600 --> 00:15:52,960
But what no one knew was,

522
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:54,720
after I stepped
onto the rotating platform,

523
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,480
(Set up the mechanism unnoticed)
I quickly took the chance

524
00:15:56,480 --> 00:15:58,200
to turn the decorative mirror

525
00:15:58,200 --> 00:15:59,960
on the pillar between me
and An Xiaoding,

526
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:02,480
so it faced the Tree of Life.

527
00:16:02,880 --> 00:16:04,560
When the shoot reached the third round,

528
00:16:04,560 --> 00:16:06,200
we noticed Uncle Er

529
00:16:06,200 --> 00:16:07,680
sitting there completely still.

530
00:16:07,680 --> 00:16:08,040
Er?

531
00:16:08,040 --> 00:16:09,720
Everyone quickly stopped to check.

532
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:11,520
He was already dead in his chair.

533
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,840
I pretended to be shocked.

534
00:16:13,900 --> 00:16:15,240
(Faking shock to cover her tracks)

535
00:16:15,240 --> 00:16:16,920
I didn't expect

536
00:16:16,920 --> 00:16:18,560
- that one small move could kill him.
- Stop filming.

537
00:16:18,560 --> 00:16:19,800
And before that,

538
00:16:19,800 --> 00:16:21,480
(Resetting the mirror to erase evidence)
I had quietly turned the mirror back.

539
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:23,160
There was a poisoned needle

540
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:23,820
near the body's heart.

541
00:16:23,820 --> 00:16:24,480
It's a needle.

542
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:25,300
(A thin needle)

543
00:16:25,480 --> 00:16:26,000
That's right.

544
00:16:26,000 --> 00:16:28,000
That was exactly part of our plan.

545
00:16:28,200 --> 00:16:30,120
But I only knew
that after turning the mirror,

546
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:32,080
a laser would reflect off the mirror

547
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:33,360
(Laser lasts 6s. Crossbow fires once)
and trigger the mechanism.

548
00:16:33,840 --> 00:16:35,880
I didn't know the movements
of my other two partners.

549
00:16:36,760 --> 00:16:37,960
(Reconstructing the method: Laser,)
After the evidence search showed

550
00:16:37,960 --> 00:16:38,840
(Needle launcher, mirror reflection)
that the poisoned-needle crossbow

551
00:16:38,840 --> 00:16:40,760
was triggered by reflected laser light,

552
00:16:41,200 --> 00:16:42,800
I tried to draw everyone's attention

553
00:16:42,800 --> 00:16:43,620
(Using unrelated items to create doubt)
toward other

554
00:16:43,620 --> 00:16:44,360
(Misleading the search to avoid risk)
unimportant mirrors.

555
00:16:44,680 --> 00:16:46,440
But the autopsy report showed

556
00:16:46,440 --> 00:16:47,440
(An Er had been electroshocked)
that besides the poisoned needle,

557
00:16:47,440 --> 00:16:49,280
An Er had also been electroshocked.

558
00:16:49,280 --> 00:16:50,880
(Had been electroshocked)
The cause of death was unknown.

559
00:16:51,360 --> 00:16:52,400
How could this be?

560
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:54,000
Someone else was trying to kill him too.

561
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,640
So I suggested

562
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:58,280
confirming the exact timing
of the poison and the electroshock

563
00:16:58,280 --> 00:16:59,120
to find out

564
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:01,080
which method actually killed him.

565
00:17:01,080 --> 00:17:02,400
If it was the electroshock,

566
00:17:02,400 --> 00:17:04,000
then I wasn't the killer.

567
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,880
Based on the clues, we worked out

568
00:17:05,880 --> 00:17:07,040
that the electroshock did come first.

569
00:17:07,040 --> 00:17:09,960
And both poison and electroshock
were done by teams of three.

570
00:17:09,960 --> 00:17:11,160
No. 1 was the planner.

571
00:17:11,520 --> 00:17:13,070
No. 2 handled the stage setup.

572
00:17:13,520 --> 00:17:16,160
No. 3 made the move
on the rotating platform.

573
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:18,680
In other words,
six people had made a move.

574
00:17:19,070 --> 00:17:19,880
But like me,

575
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,760
the other two members of Needle Team

576
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:22,640
weren't the killers either.

577
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:24,760
(Using her role to find the real killer)
An Xiaoding and I were both No. 3.

578
00:17:24,760 --> 00:17:26,310
Since I was the one
who turned the mirror

579
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:27,960
to help trigger the poisoned needle,

580
00:17:27,960 --> 00:17:29,280
then he had to be the one

581
00:17:29,280 --> 00:17:30,120
who kicked the electric wire.

582
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:31,800
During the private chat round,

583
00:17:31,800 --> 00:17:33,200
both Jin Xiangyu and He Jiahuan

584
00:17:33,200 --> 00:17:34,640
asked to speak with me privately.

585
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:35,200
I have to choose my wife.

586
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:36,400
After thinking it over,

587
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:38,040
I decided to talk to He Jiahuan first.

588
00:17:38,480 --> 00:17:40,120
He said he set up the mirror
and the crossbow.

589
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:42,040
Based on his attitude and analysis,

590
00:17:42,040 --> 00:17:43,400
(Judging by his behavior)
I chose to trust him for now.

591
00:17:43,400 --> 00:17:45,360
(Initial judgment: same side)
So we must be on Needle team.

592
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:48,320
But when Jin Xiangyu
told me very sincerely

593
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:50,000
that she had installed the mirror...

594
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,080
I installed a mirror
on the short pillar.

595
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:53,800
I started to feel torn.

596
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:55,760
I didn't know who to believe.

597
00:17:55,760 --> 00:17:57,100
(Their stories don't match)

598
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:58,520
As for User No. 1,

599
00:17:58,520 --> 00:18:00,160
was it Pai

600
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:00,800
or Mr. Wu?

601
00:18:01,520 --> 00:18:04,200
Mr. Wu had worked
in this house for many years.

602
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:05,760
The electric box was
in a more hidden spot,

603
00:18:05,760 --> 00:18:08,320
so Mr. Wu was probably
more familiar with it.

604
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:10,280
- Pai only came two months ago.
- Two months ago.

605
00:18:10,280 --> 00:18:11,260
(Based on length of service)
That made it

606
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:12,560
(Judging familiarity to identify No. 1)
less likely that she knew about it.

607
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,640
Then what did you set up?

608
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:14,640
I set up the crossbow.

609
00:18:15,760 --> 00:18:18,000
When Jin Xiangyu
privately talked to He Jiahuan,

610
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,640
he only said he had placed the crossbow.

611
00:18:19,640 --> 00:18:21,160
(Everything shows on his face)
I could only laugh helplessly.

612
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:23,120
Could He Jiahuan,
the person I had trusted all along,

613
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:24,480
be lying?

614
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:25,640
So I asked him

615
00:18:25,640 --> 00:18:26,600
if he had lied.

616
00:18:27,200 --> 00:18:28,600
(Catching the inconsistency)
Did you set that up?

617
00:18:28,600 --> 00:18:29,320
And he said

618
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:31,560
he really did handle No. 2's part.

619
00:18:31,560 --> 00:18:33,680
He explained
that since they were both No. 2,

620
00:18:33,680 --> 00:18:35,320
he couldn't tell Jin everything.

621
00:18:35,320 --> 00:18:36,520
I thought that made sense.

622
00:18:37,080 --> 00:18:39,080
I just had to turn it back at the end,

623
00:18:39,080 --> 00:18:39,680
and that was it.

624
00:18:39,680 --> 00:18:42,000
(Alert)
Right after that, An Xiaoding did claim

625
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,080
the step of turning the mirror
on the rotating platform.

626
00:18:44,560 --> 00:18:46,360
Everything Xiao Ding said was a lie.

627
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:50,040
To prove he was lying,

628
00:18:50,040 --> 00:18:51,280
I clearly pointed out

629
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:53,400
(Giving exact details as counterproof)
that the mirror had to face the Tree,

630
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:56,040
(Strengthening her innocent image)
and the laser triggered the needle.

631
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:58,320
- An Xiaoding denied knowing about it.
- There was no mention

632
00:18:58,320 --> 00:18:59,200
of anything

633
00:18:59,200 --> 00:19:00,480
other than this mirror.

634
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:01,520
(Based on task division)
That made sense,

635
00:19:01,520 --> 00:19:02,960
(Further confirm Electroshock member)
because he handled the electroshock.

636
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:05,240
He Jiahuan also backed me up.

637
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:05,800
Right.

638
00:19:06,520 --> 00:19:09,000
- After thinking for a long time,
- Let's vote.

639
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:11,200
I chose Mr. Wu,
who knew the house better, for No. 1.

640
00:19:11,200 --> 00:19:11,960
(Voting window: Mr. Wu)
For No. 2,

641
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,360
I voted for Jin Xiangyu.

642
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:14,320
(Voting window)
In the end,

643
00:19:14,320 --> 00:19:15,880
I still chose

644
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:16,960
to trust my husband,

645
00:19:16,960 --> 00:19:17,800
He Jiahuan.

646
00:19:18,380 --> 00:19:20,100
(Case Report)

647
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:22,380
(Liu Yuning's player log archived)

648
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:23,140
(Identity update: An Xiaoning)

649
00:19:23,140 --> 00:19:23,780
(Determined to polish beads
for the world)

650
00:19:23,780 --> 00:19:24,220
(Not part
of An Glass Factory's core team)

651
00:19:24,220 --> 00:19:24,700
(An Xiaoning: bead lover)

652
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,240
I'm player Liu Yuning.

653
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:30,280
In this case, I play An Xiaoning,
the eldest son of the An family.

654
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:30,980
(An Xiaoning,
eldest son of the An family)

655
00:19:31,080 --> 00:19:32,880
(An Glass Factory)
On March 24, 2016,

656
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:33,880
at 9:30 in the morning,

657
00:19:34,320 --> 00:19:35,280
I returned to the An residence

658
00:19:35,280 --> 00:19:37,040
for the magazine shoot.

659
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:39,640
When the shoot reached the third round,

660
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:41,280
Mr. An, we're about to start.

661
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:42,160
The photographer noticed

662
00:19:42,160 --> 00:19:43,920
my second uncle, An Er, wasn't moving.

663
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:44,880
Everyone stopped to check.

664
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,160
Call an ambulance!

665
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:48,040
He's dead.

666
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,200
I never expected An Er

667
00:19:51,200 --> 00:19:52,760
to die right there in his chair.

668
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:53,840
I was shocked at the time.

669
00:19:54,080 --> 00:19:56,840
We were all filming
on the same rotating platform,

670
00:19:56,840 --> 00:19:58,440
standing very close to one another.

671
00:19:58,440 --> 00:20:00,120
And the photographer was facing us too.

672
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,960
Yet the killer still managed

673
00:20:01,960 --> 00:20:03,320
to commit the crime

674
00:20:03,320 --> 00:20:05,200
silently in front of everyone.

675
00:20:05,880 --> 00:20:06,280
What is this?

676
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:07,920
It's a needle.

677
00:20:08,680 --> 00:20:11,080
(A thin needle)
I found a needle near the body's heart.

678
00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:12,160
My first thought was

679
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:14,760
(Reading scene for a hidden mechanism)
There had to be a mechanism nearby.

680
00:20:14,760 --> 00:20:16,600
Since we were all facing outward,

681
00:20:16,600 --> 00:20:18,480
the killer may have known

682
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:19,360
An Er's position in advance.

683
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:20,720
Based on where he stand,

684
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,640
the killer used a pre-set device

685
00:20:22,640 --> 00:20:24,160
(Using positions to infer death cause)
to shoot the needle and kill him.

686
00:20:24,520 --> 00:20:26,520
Sure enough,
in a potted plant in the corner,

687
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:28,920
we found the crossbow
that fired the needle.

688
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:29,480
A crossbow?

689
00:20:29,480 --> 00:20:30,280
Careful.

690
00:20:31,000 --> 00:20:34,240
The laser lasts six seconds
and can fire the crossbow.

691
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:35,560
It can only be used once.

692
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:37,220
Soon, on the phone left behind

693
00:20:37,220 --> 00:20:38,160
(Laser dot)
by the photographer,

694
00:20:38,160 --> 00:20:39,800
we found a snapshot.

695
00:20:39,800 --> 00:20:41,520
While trying to work out

696
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:43,800
(Player's view: mirror outward)
which mirror reflected the laser,

697
00:20:43,800 --> 00:20:45,320
(Photographer's view: mirror inward)
I thought of a possibility.

698
00:20:45,320 --> 00:20:46,880
Maybe the killer had brought

699
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:47,640
a small mirror.

700
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:48,890
Guessing the method based on clues)
Or maybe this one could...

701
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:51,200
But once we touched that platform,

702
00:20:51,200 --> 00:20:52,800
we found it could be removed
and moved around.

703
00:20:52,800 --> 00:20:54,200
So only this piece can be removed?

704
00:20:54,200 --> 00:20:54,880
Out of all the platforms,

705
00:20:54,880 --> 00:20:56,840
only that one could be moved.

706
00:20:56,960 --> 00:20:58,520
So among the people standing there,

707
00:20:58,520 --> 00:21:00,680
(Movable mirror)
either An Xiaoding or An Xiaowen

708
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:03,250
(Mechanism location narrows suspects)
had made the move.

709
00:21:03,880 --> 00:21:04,960
There were accomplices.

710
00:21:04,960 --> 00:21:07,000
Later, through evidence and deduction,

711
00:21:07,000 --> 00:21:09,720
we figured out that three people
were needed to trigger the mechanism.

712
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,760
Autopsy report)
And another three-person team

713
00:21:11,760 --> 00:21:13,440
(An Er had been electroshocked)
had also made a move using electricity.

714
00:21:13,440 --> 00:21:14,400
Further examination showed

715
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:16,920
that the victim, An Er,
had been electroshocked.

716
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:17,920
Two groups of people.

717
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:20,280
They weren't working
with the same level of detail,

718
00:21:20,280 --> 00:21:21,360
but they acted at the same time.

719
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:22,280
They all wanted him dead.

720
00:21:22,280 --> 00:21:24,360
(Combining the existing clues)
All six suspects had made a move.

721
00:21:24,360 --> 00:21:25,040
(Suspecting group-based murders)

722
00:21:25,040 --> 00:21:25,920
Assassin.

723
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:26,960
(Killer Empire, Little Assassin Zone:
dark web rewind）

724
00:21:26,960 --> 00:21:28,120
Found it.

725
00:21:28,120 --> 00:21:29,440
My method can be split into three steps.

726
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:30,440
Each of us takes one step.

727
00:21:30,440 --> 00:21:32,240
That way, we can all clear ourselves.

728
00:21:32,240 --> 00:21:33,680
Let's talk tonight
using a voice changer.

729
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:36,200
It's the same.

730
00:21:36,200 --> 00:21:37,680
(Page 3, Page 4)
We finally confirmed

731
00:21:37,680 --> 00:21:39,520
on the Assassin Forum

732
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:41,880
(Different IDs)
that there were two teams of three.

733
00:21:41,880 --> 00:21:43,240
We also saw how they divided the work.

734
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:43,920
They were all different.

735
00:21:44,120 --> 00:21:45,640
Actually, back then,

736
00:21:45,640 --> 00:21:47,960
another post on the forum
caught my attention.

737
00:21:47,960 --> 00:21:49,360
(Killer Empire, Little Assassin Zone)
A 188 cm, 75 kg,

738
00:21:49,360 --> 00:21:51,520
slightly handsome rookie male assassin

739
00:21:51,520 --> 00:21:53,280
has never had a girlfriend.
Is that normal?

740
00:21:53,280 --> 00:21:54,640
Which one of you three is it?

741
00:21:54,640 --> 00:21:55,360
188 cm.

742
00:21:56,280 --> 00:21:57,380
(Digging beyond the obvious clues)
I had always had questions

743
00:21:57,380 --> 00:21:58,240
(Completing the deduction)
about this post.

744
00:21:58,280 --> 00:22:00,280
When everyone already
had someone in mind

745
00:22:00,280 --> 00:22:01,400
and started voting,

746
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:02,240
(Voting window)

747
00:22:02,240 --> 00:22:04,040
I stayed behind
to keep checking that post.

748
00:22:04,100 --> 00:22:04,780
(Carefully reviewing the evidence)

749
00:22:04,780 --> 00:22:06,560
(Linking it to the existing clues)
I read every single reply carefully.

750
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:09,080
Gradually, I noticed
that the gender clues

751
00:22:09,080 --> 00:22:10,560
(Identifying him as male)
in the post were very clear.

752
00:22:10,560 --> 00:22:11,720
Because our suspects

753
00:22:11,720 --> 00:22:12,640
(Identifying her as female)
were also three men and three women.

754
00:22:13,000 --> 00:22:14,560
Let's see if you're as handsome as me.

755
00:22:14,560 --> 00:22:15,120
I'll let my girlfriend judge.

756
00:22:15,120 --> 00:22:16,120
(Identifying him as male)
So this one must be male.

757
00:22:16,440 --> 00:22:18,280
Based on these few replies,

758
00:22:18,280 --> 00:22:19,600
(Identifying gender through speech)
we could tell their genders.

759
00:22:19,600 --> 00:22:20,840
For all the male nicknames,

760
00:22:20,840 --> 00:22:23,040
the second-to-last digit was odd.

761
00:22:23,040 --> 00:22:25,800
(Male: odd. Female: even)
For the female nicknames, it was even.

762
00:22:25,800 --> 00:22:27,180
(Using hidden gender information)
So I went back

763
00:22:27,180 --> 00:22:28,680
(to identify the group lists)
to check the two groups' nicknames.

764
00:22:28,680 --> 00:22:29,920
(Group 1: Mr. Wu, Jin Xiangyu, An Xiaowen)
I got two groups.

765
00:22:29,920 --> 00:22:32,320
(Group 2: Pai, He Jiahuan, An Xiaoding)
Mr. Wu, Jin Xiangyu, and An Xiaowen.

766
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:35,360
Pai, He Jiahuan, and An Xiaoding.

767
00:22:35,520 --> 00:22:36,920
Because during the group discussion,

768
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,200
everyone had reached a consensus.

769
00:22:38,760 --> 00:22:39,720
Wu is Electroshock.

770
00:22:39,720 --> 00:22:40,560
Okay.

771
00:22:40,560 --> 00:22:41,720
Yes.

772
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,680
Mr. Wu knew the house better.

